# Project-specific
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Data — never commit raw filings, indexes, or eval outputs to git
data/raw/
data/processed/
data/indexes/
data/eval_runs/
!data/.gitkeep

# Eval QA dataset is the only data artifact we DO track (small, hand-curated)
!data/qa_dataset/

